query:
/*+  */ select acc.location,
count(*)
from question AS q1
inner join tag_question AS tq1
on q1.id = tq1.question_id AND q1.favorite_count >= 0 AND q1.favorite_count <= 1
inner join tag AS t1
on t1.id = tq1.tag_id AND t1.name IN ('7',
'8',
'beginner',
'c++',
'java',
'javascript',
'python',
'views')
inner join answer AS a1
on q1.id = a1.question_id
inner join site AS s
on s.site_id = t1.site_id AND s.site_id = a1.site_id AND s.site_id = q1.site_id AND s.site_id = tq1.site_id AND s.site_name IN ('codereview',
'drupal')
inner join badge AS b
on s.site_id = b.site_id AND b.name IN ('Analytical',
'Benefactor',
'Critic',
'Curious',
'Enthusiast',
'Excavator',
'Nice Answer',
'Organizer',
'Peer Pressure',
'Quorum',
'Revival',
'Self-Learner')
inner join so_user AS u1
on s.site_id = u1.site_id AND a1.owner_user_id = u1.id AND b.user_id = u1.id AND u1.downvotes >= 0 AND u1.downvotes <= 1
inner join account AS acc
on acc.id = u1.account_id group by acc.location order by count(*) desc LIMIT 100;
